- When working with the database, always use the Supabase MCP (Multi-Cloud Platform) server that has been installed:

  - For database queries and operations, connect through the Supabase MCP server instead of direct database access
  - This applies to all database checks, reads, writes, and administrative operations
  - The MCP server handles connection pooling, security, and performance optimization
  

- Benefits of using Supabase MCP:
  - Consistent security policies
  - Connection pooling and optimization
  - Built-in caching
  - Real-time capabilities
  - Row Level Security enforcement
  - Audit logging
